    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/25750596/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_8892017868185054718.png",
                "id": "talent82156",
                "key": "Favonius Bladework - Edel",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Favonius Bladework - Edel"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. Memberikan status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grimheart</span> pada Karakter ini jika belum memiliki status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grimheart</span>.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Grimheart </span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>Saat <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Karakter yang terpengaruh melancarkan Icetide Vortex: </span>Status ini akan dihapus dan mengakibatkan +3 poin DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/27/25750596/78b526224710dda639b49972145339a9_1389168371365594861.png",
                "id": "talent64792",
                "key": "Icetide Vortex",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Icetide Vortex"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Lightfall Sword</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/27/25750596/72b7716be67efac4ec94efde16957180_5185935620634650029.png",
                "id": "talent56784",
                "key": "Glacial Illumination",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Glacial Illumination"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Eula menggunakan Normal Attack atau Elemental Skill:</span> Kartu ini mendapatkan 2 Lapisan Zeal, tetapi Eula tidak akan mendapatkan Energy.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Kartu ini akan dibuang dan mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>. Setiap Lapisan Zeal akan mengakibatkan DMG +1.</p><p>(Efek yang memengaruhi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan </span>kartu ini akan diterapkan ke <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lapisan Zeal</span>.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1494109459692345110.png",
                "id": "talent65065",
                "key": "Lightfall Sword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/27/25750596/3f07051befd3fcb50000df92021710d6_8972127212331267863.png",
                "title": "Lightfall Sword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/25750596/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_7571001062138126041.png",
                "id": "talent8340",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/27/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3728370342221309332.png",
                "id": "talent3307",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
